{"tid":139400,"cid":23,"subCid":0,"title":"相機同鏡頭防潮一問","createTime":"2017-03-01T11:29:24.000Z","updateTime":"2017-03-05T18:54:00.000Z","uid":78620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"41bab9ae9becff925faa1f7bbcd0576f2a407b4a","tid":139400,"uid":78620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T11:29:24.000Z","msg":"如果我去家品店買40幾蚊防潮膠箱, 定期換下D防潮珠, 唔知夠唔夠用黎防發霉?<br />\n<br />\n利申: 無相機, 諗住買一機一鏡但唔知點保養先夠"},{"pid":"8fc7655d1c1042922b568cbe7f8d9552539e013a","tid":139400,"uid":78620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T11:43:20.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"1dc54e839e0ee11feb19054c1d97dd3e3e2b5579","tid":139400,"uid":6981,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T11:43:52.000Z","msg":"治標唔治本<br />\n<br />\n頂得一時 頂唔得耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"0677032c22dfa9fd9d9439e554697b74624e8810","tid":139400,"uid":78620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T12:23:32.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>治標唔治本<br />\n<br />\n頂得一時 頂唔得耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n姐係一定要買果D電動防潮箱<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?"},{"pid":"d420dae17bed86683c8c0d7344bd43af50f42729","tid":139400,"uid":7369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T12:25:16.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>治標唔治本<br />\n<br />\n頂得一時 頂唔得耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n姐係一定要買果D電動防潮箱<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我個電子防潮箱用左六年都未壞，$6-700蚊一個抵用啦"},{"pid":"ac04389fa18c14da2cafcdc1bbae70189c7c4c8d","tid":139400,"uid":78620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T12:26:52.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>治標唔治本<br />\n<br />\n頂得一時 頂唔得耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n姐係一定要買果D電動防潮箱<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我個電子防潮箱用左六年都未壞，$6-700蚊一個抵用啦</blockquote><br />\n錢都係其次, 我驚無位存放<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"9bfcb23cb47c2e6a120cfcecfd8ed2b89e533029","tid":139400,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T12:33:47.000Z","msg":"如果回南天你只係用防潮珠未必夠力<br />\n可能放兩個鐘已經轉色<br />\n<br />\n除非密封得好好<br />\n咁先抽乾再冚好啦<br />\n<br />\n就算吸濕咭原理亦一樣<br />\n你一日可能要換好多次<br />\n<br />\n樓主你個case我曾經試過<br />\n我用放衣櫃濕左變啫喱狀果種<br />\n當然會耐用少少但是新放入去果陣就會抽得好乾"},{"pid":"bab62b7d89f1214a2aad5e74c68f5337efbb35c4","tid":139400,"uid":7369,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T12:35:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>治標唔治本<br />\n<br />\n頂得一時 頂唔得耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n姐係一定要買果D電動防潮箱<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我個電子防潮箱用左六年都未壞，$6-700蚊一個抵用啦</blockquote><br />\n錢都係其次, 我驚無位存放<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n<br />\n你用膠箱都會佔位啦，而且仲可以放埋其他電子野（我老婆連封淨嘅利是錢都放埋入去<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/clown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ）"},{"pid":"0dbb0c9bcb72bbd6045647a28e7d38fcbd4a8adf","tid":139400,"uid":78620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T12:40:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>治標唔治本<br />\n<br />\n頂得一時 頂唔得耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n姐係一定要買果D電動防潮箱<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我個電子防潮箱用左六年都未壞，$6-700蚊一個抵用啦</blockquote><br />\n錢都係其次, 我驚無位存放<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我見電子防潮箱好似要插電, 又好似大舊D, <br />\n有無D可以放係櫃仔入面嘅電子防潮箱<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?"},{"pid":"7104309b08ec41c4e8ebb9b74b6d75f4378c2103","tid":139400,"uid":52056,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T14:10:41.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote><blockquote>治標唔治本<br />\n<br />\n頂得一時 頂唔得耐<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n姐係一定要買果D電動防潮箱<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n我個電子防潮箱用左六年都未壞，$6-700蚊一個抵用啦</blockquote><br />\n錢都係其次, 我驚無位存放<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我見電子防潮箱好似要插電, 又好似大舊D, <br />\n有無D可以放係櫃仔入面嘅電子防潮箱<img src=\"/assets/faces/fs/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> ?</blockquote><br />\n有我都想要<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />冇位緊要過冇錢<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/sosad.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /><br />\n不過唔插電應該冇辦法keep住濕度"},{"pid":"a72f6ebbe4cca69a53f1612f117b10f9af20df7b","tid":139400,"uid":26080,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T15:02:58.000Z","msg":"試過買日本城膠盒（聲稱密封）、濕度計、防潮珠諗住自制，但係太難控制個濕度，最後都係買電子防潮箱"},{"pid":"e9fade10f653c1e06f5619955318ef87ee98732e","tid":139400,"uid":7378,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T15:09:38.000Z","msg":"其實常常拎出街用更加重要"},{"pid":"ce665d01d07cfac404d17842538da6dce5915c8c","tid":139400,"uid":78620,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T15:13:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>其實常常拎出街用更加重要</blockquote><br />\n如果日日拎出街用, 部機係咪都應該存放入防潮箱?"},{"pid":"9cff7a6965b64d18910402f0efbfdb2d8809e305","tid":139400,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-03-01T15:34:25.000Z","msg":"<blockquote><blockquote>其實常常拎出街用更加重要</blockquote><br />\n如果日日拎出街用, 部機係咪都應該存放入防潮箱?</blockquote><br />\n<br />\n如果幾日我會放，至少唔洗舖塵。<br />\n聽日就用的話我直接放袋。"},{"pid":"aaa500258999e1ea359dbf6f2d1188d20bdcf617","tid":139400,"uid":36157,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score